title: Samsung Dishwasher Installation Bracket
description: Samsung Dishwasher Installation Bracket PartSelect Number PS10058975 Manufacturer Part Number DD61-00465A This genuine OEM installation bracket, or mounting bracket, anchors the appliance to the surrounding cabinets, so that it stays in place and does not shift during operation. They hold the unit under the countertop. Keep in mind that this replacement part is sold individually, so check how many you will need for your installation.
